Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Primary battle reaching climax
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z9b58
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Jun 1976
Both parties tense as presidential primaries reach climax with the Californian vote. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.